From 3ae4cb9b2d5c187267eed1669f37c4d134738874 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: DGX Spark Dev <dev@dgx-spark.local>
Date: Sun, 12 Apr 2026 19:31:44 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] feat(loader): add DGX Spark unified memory optimizations to
 Instruct loader

Add background page cache dropper during from_pretrained() that periodically
drops OS page cache for safetensors shards every 30s, preventing ~83GB of
mmap'd page cache from accumulating on unified memory systems. Replace manual
time.sleep(15) hack with programmatic page cache management. Replace raw
torch.cuda.empty_cache() with soft_empty_cache_unified() and add memory
observability via memory_report()/memory_delta().

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
